NK037(ji)005:1: // mgon po tshogs kyi bdag po'i mngon rtogs drag sngags gsang ba spu gri'i rgyud bzhugs so //
NK037(ji)005:2: mgon po spyan ras gzigs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)005:3: de yi spyan sngar dam bcas pa'i //
NK037(ji)005:4: chos skyong tshogs bdag legs ldan sras //
NK037(ji)005:6: lnga brgya dus kyi snyigs ma la //
NK037(ji)005:7: las kyi sdang ba'i bstan dgra rnams //
NK037(ji)005:8: tshang bcad bkug bsad brlag pa'i thabs //
NK037(ji)005:9: bee ro tsa na'i snyan brgyud pa //
NK037(ji)005:10: drag sngags gsang ba'i spu gri yi //
NK037(ji)005:11: sgrub thabs sbyor dngos rjes gsum mo //
NK037(ji)005:12: dang po sbyor ba bcas kyi rim pa ni /
NK037(ji)005:13: sa sna gdug pa can la mdun tu man+dala gru bzhi tshad dang ldan pa bcas la /
NK037(ji)005:14: de'i steng du mi shis pa'i sa sna tshogs la /
NK037(ji)005:15: gru gsum rgyar khru gang ba /
NK037(ji)005:17: de'i nang du dug khrag sna tshogs kyis byug /
NK037(ji)005:18: rgyab tu ro sol nag pos byugs la man+dala gyi steng du bzhag /
NK037(ji)005:19: de nas ling+ga tshul bzhin du bris la 'bod rbad bsad gsum gyi sngags kyis bskor /
NK037(ji)005:20: gnas gsum du skyer phur gsum btsugs /
NK037(ji)005:21: dbyer dgug bsad gsum rgyas par byas la ro ltebs byed /
NK037(ji)005:22: gru gu sngon dmar gyis bcing /
NK037(ji)005:23: khyi ra phag gsum gang rung gi thod par bcug la thun khung nang du bzhag /
NK037(ji)005:24: mgon po'i tsaka li rab gnas dang ldan pa dbus su btsugs /
NK037(ji)005:25: g.yas zur du sku mchog tsaka li /
NK037(ji)005:26: g.yon zur du gsung mchog tsaka li /
NK037(ji)005:27: rgyab tu thugs mchog tsaka li bcas zur gsum du btsugs /
NK037(ji)005:28: yum gyi tsaka li yab kyi g.yon zur du gtsugs /
NK037(ji)005:29: de'i phyi ril du mgo brnyan gyi tshogs kyis bskor /
NK037(ji)005:30: der ma tshud na gru gsum gyi rgyab tu bskor /
NK037(ji)005:31: thun thag mdun du phur pa la btod /
NK037(ji)005:32: de rgyab drag po'i rtsang sum cu rtsa dagu'am /
NK037(ji)005:33: nyer gcig gis srin mo'i 'gros su bskor /
NK037(ji)005:34: de rgyab drag po'i shing gi rkang gsum dang /
NK037(ji)005:35: dar nag gam re ba'i gur phub /
NK037(ji)005:36: de nas yi dam chos skyong gi mchod gtor rgyas par bsham /
NK037(ji)005:37: mgon po'i gtor ma g.yag snying lta bu la sdong sol gyis nag por byugs la snod du bsham /
NK037(ji)005:38: ngos gsum du bshos phran gsum bsham /
NK037(ji)005:39: g.yag lug gi stod shas brgyan la rkang gsum gyi khar bzhag /
NK037(ji)005:40: srog rten dar nag po la ma h+aa k+aa la'i sku'am snying po bris la btsugs /
NK037(ji)005:41: tsan+da gyi bing la dar sna tshogs dang rin po che sna tshogs kyis brgyan la rten du btsugs /
NK037(ji)005:42: sku mchog gi rten du rta nag gi tsit+ta /
NK037(ji)005:43: gsung mchog gi rten du lug nag gi tsit+ta /
NK037(ji)005:44: thugs mchog gi rten du g.yag nag gi tsit+ta /
NK037(ji)005:45: phyogs bcu mgon po'i don du bya rgod mda' dar /
NK037(ji)005:46: rkang gsum gyi khar ram gang bder gzugs 'gros bsham pa ni /
NK037(ji)005:47: bya rgyal khyung chen la sogs pa'i 'dab chags /
NK037(ji)005:52: gzhan yang gzhung las gang grags rnams bsham /
NK037(ji)005:53: thun rdzas ni yungs kar nag la sogs pa'i dug rigs sna tshogs dang /
NK037(ji)005:54: zangs phye lcags phye sna tshogs 'tshags /
NK037(ji)005:55: gzhan yang sgrub pa ma rdzogs kyi bar du mkho ba'i yo byad rnams bsham /
NK037(ji)005:56: de ni sbyor ba bcas kyi rim pa'o //
NK037(ji)005:57: spyi don gnyis pa dngos gzhi nyams su len pa'i
NK037(ji)005:58: rim pa la bcu'i dang po rten gzhal yas khang
NK037(ji)005:59: gdan dang bcas pa bskyed pa ni /
NK037(ji)005:60: dang po bsang mchod dang chab gtor rgyas par bsngosa la /
NK037(ji)005:62: mthun rkyen myur du 'grub pa'i sdong grogs mdzod cig /
NK037(ji)005:64: phyi rigs la yang dkar gtor bsngo la /
NK037(ji)005:66: srung ma pho rgyud mo rgyud 'khor dang bcas pa khyed rnams kyis gzu dpang mdzod /
NK037(ji)005:71: nyes byed la chad pas chod cig /
NK037(ji)005:73: phur pa ma h+aa k+aa lar bsgom /
NK037(ji)005:74: dam 'dogs la sogs rgyas par byed /
NK037(ji)005:75: nam mkha' bar snang sa gzhi brtag pa rnams bya'o //
NK037(ji)005:76: de nas yi dam chos skyong gi bsnyen mchod dang /
NK037(ji)005:77: skong bshags tshogs mchod rnams rgyas par bya'o //
NK037(ji)005:79: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+hahsarba d+har+m+aahswa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho &aham /
NK037(ji)005:80: mdun gyi bcas rnams mi dmigs pa stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK037(ji)005:82: rang nyid yi dam gyi thugs ka nas t+r+aam gcig
NK037(ji)005:83: 'phros pa 'od du zhu ba las rin po che
NK037(ji)005:84: sna bzhi las grub pa'i ri rab dbyibs gru bzhi
NK037(ji)005:85: bang rim gsum dang ldan pa /
NK037(ji)005:86: de'i steng du pad+ma r+aa ga'i thig bkye ba'i thog
NK037(ji)005:87: tu b+h+r+aum las rin po che sna tshogs las grub
NK037(ji)005:88: pa'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi sgo khyud
NK037(ji)005:89: dang ldan pa / gser gyi ka ba la g.yu yi gdung ma bres pa /
NK037(ji)005:90: rgyan rta babs chos 'khor bang rim tog dang ri dwags gdugs dang bcas pa'o //
NK037(ji)005:91: de'i nang du chos bzang lha'i 'dun sa a mo li ka'i rdo leb mdog nya phyis lta bu /
NK037(ji)005:92: de'i dbus su gru gsum mthing nag yangs shing rgya che ba /
NK037(ji)005:97: sod sod dang chod chod kyi sgra sgrogs pa /
NK037(ji)005:98: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyi 'dus sa /
NK037(ji)005:99: bka'i lha ma srin sde brgyad kyi rgyug srang /
NK037(ji)005:100: stod na zhe sdang gi me 'bar ba /
NK037(ji)005:101: smad na 'dod chags kyi khrag mtsho 'khyil ba /
NK037(ji)005:102: bar na phrag dog gi rlung nag 'tshubs pa /
NK037(ji)005:103: gshin rje'i bshas khang nag po /
NK037(ji)005:104: rngams 'thug la bong mtho ba logs gzar ba /
NK037(ji)005:105: de'i nang du lcags sreg ngar ma'i sa gzhi chen po'i steng du /
NK037(ji)005:106: n+ri yongs su gyur pa las /
NK037(ji)005:107: dgra bo gan rkyal du mgo tshur bstan te rkang pa phyir brkyang ba /
NK037(ji)005:108: kha nas smre sngags sna tshogs 'don pa /
NK037(ji)005:109: gcer bu mgon skyabs med pa 'dar phri li li byed pa /
NK037(ji)005:110: de'i thog tu gnam lcags kyi 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad
NK037(ji)005:111: pa dmar lhang nge bas bkab pa las mtshon cha
NK037(ji)005:112: sna tshogs kyi char mgar gyi tsh+wa tsh+wa ltar 'bab
NK037(ji)005:113: pa / de'i steng du rdo rje rgya gram nag pos mnan pa'i lte ba'i steng du /
NK037(ji)005:114: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta s+t+wam b+ha ya nan /
NK037(ji)005:115: rwa bzhi la lam h'u lam sum lam s+t+wam b+ha ya nan gyis mtshan pa'o //
NK037(ji)005:116: de'i steng du pam las pad+ma dmar po 'dab ma brgyad pa /
NK037(ji)005:117: de'i steng du a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor bsil zer dang ldan pa /
NK037(ji)005:118: de'i steng du ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor tsha ngar dang ldan pa /
NK037(ji)005:119: gru gsum gyi rgyab tu khrag gi zla gam dmar
NK037(ji)005:120: po gsum dang ldan pa las gri gug gi phreng
NK037(ji)005:121: bas bskor ba / de'i phyi rol du 'khor lo
NK037(ji)005:122: sngon po rtsibs bcu pa mu khyud dmar pos bskor
NK037(ji)005:123: bas bskor ba / ba / de'i phyi rol tu
NK037(ji)005:124: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa mu khyud ser pos bskor
NK037(ji)005:125: bas bskor ba / ba / ba / de rgyab gru chad bzhi ni /
NK037(ji)005:126: shar gyi gru chad dmar po /
NK037(ji)005:130: mu khyud dmar pos bskor ba /
NK037(ji)005:131: de'i dbus su bi n+aa ya ka pho mo byi chings su bsnol ba'i steng du /
NK037(ji)005:132: gnyis pa dam tshig dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK037(ji)005:133: rang nyid yi dam gyi thugs ka nas h'u mthing nag gcig spros te babs /
NK037(ji)005:134: de las 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phros pas dgra bgegs gdug pa can rnams tshar bcad /
NK037(ji)005:135: sems can thams cad kyi lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgrib pa sbyangs nas /
NK037(ji)005:136: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs la mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'phul /
NK037(ji)005:137: 'jig rten 'jig rten las 'das pa'i srung ma pho
NK037(ji)005:138: rgyud thams cad kyi thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul nas
NK037(ji)005:139: / de dag thams cad kyi byin rlabs nus mthu
NK037(ji)005:140: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi dngos grub
NK037(ji)005:141: srog gi snying po dang bcas pa bsdus nas tshur
NK037(ji)005:143: h'u yongs su gyur pa las tsan+dana gyi bing sngon
NK037(ji)005:144: po zur brgyad pa'i lte ba la h'u mthing nag
NK037(ji)005:145: gis mtshan pa / yar rtse la 'brug stong ldir ba /
NK037(ji)005:146: mar rtse la glog stong 'gyu ba /
NK037(ji)005:147: lcim bzhog brgyad la lha dmag bye ba dung phyur shong ba gcig tu gyur /
NK037(ji)005:148: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la h'u phata /
NK037(ji)005:150: bing yongs su gyur pa las /
NK037(ji)005:151: mgon po legs ldan gyi sras ma h+aa k+aa la
NK037(ji)005:152: mthu bo che sku mdog mthing nag char sprin nag
NK037(ji)005:154: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum mche ba bzhi gtsigs pa /
NK037(ji)005:155: ljags 'dril sma ra smin ma ag tshom me ltar 'bar ba /
NK037(ji)005:156: dbu skra dmar ser gyen du bardzesa pa /
NK037(ji)005:157: sku gtum la zhal rngams pa /
NK037(ji)005:158: sku las mtshon cha'i ba spu skyes pa /
NK037(ji)005:160: lte ba zur gsum zab pa /
NK037(ji)005:161: dbu skra'i mtshams su thod skam lnga dang sbrul dang rin po ches brgyan pa /
NK037(ji)005:162: stag lpags rlon pa'i sham thabs byas pa /
NK037(ji)005:163: sku la dar nag gi 'jol ber gsol ba las
NK037(ji)005:164: g.yung drung ris dang tshom bu ris kyi me tog
NK037(ji)005:165: bkra ba / gser dang rin po che'i ska rags bcings pa /
NK037(ji)005:166: zhabs la sag ti'i lhwam po che mnabs pa /
NK037(ji)005:167: thod rlon lnga bcu rtsa gcig gi phreng ba se ral khar thogs pa /
NK037(ji)005:168: phyag g.yas tsan+dana gyi bing sngon po zur brgyad pa phyar thabs su bsnams pa /
NK037(ji)005:169: g.yon pas thod khrag thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK037(ji)005:170: bskal pa'i me rlung 'tshubs pa'i klong na 'gying bag gi tshul du bzhugs pa /
NK037(ji)005:171: de'i dung khang nang du zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du dkar po /
NK037(ji)005:172: mgrin par pad+ma'i steng du +aahdamara po /
NK037(ji)005:173: thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du tsan+dana gyi bing sngon
NK037(ji)005:174: po tshon gang ba'i lte ba la h'u mthing nag
NK037(ji)005:175: gis mtshan pa / de'i mthar bskor du /
NK037(ji)005:176: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la h'u phata /
NK037(ji)005:177: ma h+aa k+aa la sid+d+hi yam du dzah zhes pas g.yas su 'khor ba'o //
NK037(ji)005:180: ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du dgongs
NK037(ji)005:181: 'dus po ti dang phyag na rdo rje bzhugs pa'o
NK037(ji)005:182: // de'i spyi bor pam las pad+ma a las zla
NK037(ji)005:183: ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du spyan ras gzigs bzhugs
NK037(ji)005:184: // pa'o // mgon po'i thugs ka'i h'u las b+h+yo smug nag gcig 'phros te /
NK037(ji)005:185: g.yon phyogs su rlung nag 'tshubs ma'i dbus su /
NK037(ji)005:186: dgra bo gan rkyal du bsgyel nas yod pa'i steng du bab /
NK037(ji)005:187: de las 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phros pas /
NK037(ji)005:188: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i ma mo
NK037(ji)005:189: dang mkha' 'gro ma thams cad kyi thugs dam gyi
NK037(ji)005:190: rgyud bskul nas / de dag thams cad kyi byin
NK037(ji)005:191: rlabs nus mthu sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK037(ji)005:192: kyi dngos grub srog gi snying po dang bcas pa
NK037(ji)005:193: thams cad bsdus nas tshur 'dus b+h+yo la thim /
NK037(ji)005:194: badz+ra yak+sha be t+aa li h'u /
NK037(ji)005:196: b+h+yo yongs su gyur pa las /
NK037(ji)005:197: yum yak+sha be t+aa li sku mdog nag mo char sprin gyi mdog lta bu /
NK037(ji)005:198: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK037(ji)005:199: dbu skra kham nag sa la bshal ba /
NK037(ji)005:200: spyi bor zla ba tshes shing lte bar nyi ma shar ba /
NK037(ji)005:201: sku la mkha' 'gro ma'i chas kyis brgyan pa /
NK037(ji)005:202: phyag g.yas gri gug nam mkhar phyar ba /
NK037(ji)005:203: g.yon pas thod khrag thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK037(ji)005:204: rlung nag 'tshubs ma'i nang du chibs su drel rta
NK037(ji)005:205: gwa pa la zhon pa rgyan cha lugs dang ldan
NK037(ji)005:206: par bskyed do // thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du b+h+yo smug nag la /
NK037(ji)005:207: badz+ra yak+sha be t+aa li h'u /
NK037(ji)005:208: trag rak+sha rag mo thum ril snying la 'dus 'dus /
NK037(ji)005:209: srog la bring bring sham sham khyer b+h+yo /
NK037(ji)005:211: 'khor ni 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i
NK037(ji)005:212: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro ma'i tshogs kyis bskor nas
NK037(ji)005:213: bzhugs pa'o // mgon po'i thugs ka'i h'u las h'u gsum 'phros te /
NK037(ji)005:214: zla gam gsum gyi steng du bab /
NK037(ji)005:215: de yongs su gyur pa las /
NK037(ji)005:216: g.yas kyi zla gam gyi steng du mgon po sku
NK037(ji)005:217: mchog sku mdog sngo skya zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan
NK037(ji)005:218: gsum mche ba bzhi gtsigs pa /
NK037(ji)005:219: dbu skra dmar ser gyen du bardzesa pa /
NK037(ji)005:220: sku gtum la zhal rngams pa gzi brjid dang ldan pa /
NK037(ji)005:221: phyag g.yas pas tri shul rtse gsum /
NK037(ji)005:222: g.yon pas thod khrag thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK037(ji)005:223: rgyan cha lugs gtso bo dang mthun pa /
NK037(ji)005:224: 'khor ni sku'i rigs kyi mgon po dang /
NK037(ji)005:225: khro bo dang khro mo'i tshogs kyis bskor ba'o //
NK037(ji)005:226: g.yon gyi zla gam gyi steng du mgon po gsung
NK037(ji)005:227: mchog sku mdog dmar skya zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan
NK037(ji)005:228: gsum mche ba bzhi gtsigs pa /
NK037(ji)005:229: dbu skra dmar ser gyen du bardzesa pa /
NK037(ji)005:230: sku gtum la zhal rngams pa gzi brjid dang ldan pa /
NK037(ji)005:231: phyag g.yas na tsan+dana gyi bing chen po /
NK037(ji)005:232: g.yon pas thod khrag zhal du gsol ba /
NK037(ji)005:233: rgyan cha lugs gtso bo dang mthun pa /
NK037(ji)005:234: 'khor ni gsung gi rigs kyi mgon po dang lha dmag gi tshogs kyi bskor ba'o //
NK037(ji)005:235: mdun gyi zla gam gyi steng du mgon po thugs
NK037(ji)005:236: mchog sku mdog mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan
NK037(ji)005:237: gsum mche ba bzhi gtsigs pa /
NK037(ji)005:238: dbu skra dmar ser me ltar 'bar ba /
NK037(ji)005:239: sku gtum la zhal rngams pa gzi brjid dang ldan pa /
NK037(ji)005:240: phyag g.yas pas gri gug nam mkhar phyar ba /
NK037(ji)005:241: g.yon pas thod khrag thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK037(ji)005:242: rgyan cha lugs gtso bo dang mthun pa /
NK037(ji)005:243: 'khor ni thugs kyi rigs kyi mgon po dang nag po stong sha za 'bum gyis bskor ba /
NK037(ji)005:244: de gsum gyi thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du h'u mthing nag la /
NK037(ji)005:245: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la h'u phata /
NK037(ji)005:247: gtso 'khor de dag bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i nang du zhabs gnyis 'dor thabs su bzhugs pa'o //
NK037(ji)005:248: de'i phyi rol du 'khor lo sngon po rtsibs bcu'i steng du /
NK037(ji)005:249: shar du dpal rab 'chang ba'i mgon po sku mdog
NK037(ji)005:250: smug nag phyag na nyi zer gyi zhags pa bsnams
NK037(ji)005:251: pa / lhor legs ldan gyi mgon po sku mdog
NK037(ji)005:252: mthing nag phyag na tsan+dana gyi bing sngon po zur
NK037(ji)005:253: brgyad pa phyar thabs su bsnams pa /
NK037(ji)005:254: nub tu brag lha mgon po sku mdog dmar nag phyag na tsan+dana gyi bing gru tshad bsnams pa /
NK037(ji)005:255: byang du mgon po rnam sras sku mdog ser po phyag na rgyal mtshan dang ne'u le bsnams pa /
NK037(ji)005:256: shar lhor dpal +aar+ya dza b+ha la sku mdog sngon
NK037(ji)005:257: po beed+aur+ya yi mdog lta bu phyag na ne'u le
NK037(ji)005:259: lho nub tu nyi ma'i sras po re man+ta sku
NK037(ji)005:260: mdog ser nag phyag na ru mtshon 'bar ba bsnams
NK037(ji)005:261: pa / nub byang du nag po chen po sha
NK037(ji)005:262: ba ri sku mdog ljang gu 'jigs pa'i gzugs can
NK037(ji)005:263: pa / / phyag na rma bya'i rgyal mtshan phyar ba /
NK037(ji)005:264: byang shar du rnam par snang mdzad dbu rgyan can sku mdog dkar po 'od zer 'phro ba /
NK037(ji)005:265: phyag na ru mtshon dkar po bsnams pa /
NK037(ji)005:266: shar stod du steng gi mgon po dung gi thor
NK037(ji)005:267: tshugs can phyag na gnam lcags kyi ral gri 'debs
NK037(ji)005:268: pa / nub smad du 'og phyogs kyi mgon po
NK037(ji)005:269: rak+sha sh+r+ai ya be t+aa li sku mdog nag po
NK037(ji)005:270: pa / / phyag na gnam lcags kyi s+t+wa re phyar ba /
NK037(ji)005:271: thams cad kyang rgyan cha lugs so sor ldan zhing
NK037(ji)005:272: rang rang gi sras dang btsun mo g.yog 'khor bcas
NK037(ji)005:273: pa'o // de'i phyi rol du 'khor lo sngon po rtsibs brgyad la /
NK037(ji)005:274: shar phyogs su srid pa lha'i gtso bo sku mdog
NK037(ji)005:275: dkar po sku la dar dkar gyi go zu gsol
NK037(ji)005:276: ba / g.yas na shes rab kyi ral gri phyar ba /
NK037(ji)005:277: g.yon pas dar mdung dkar po bsnams pa /
NK037(ji)005:278: chibs su lha g.yag dkar po la chibs pa /
NK037(ji)005:279: lha dmag 'bum gyi 'khor gyis bskor ba /
NK037(ji)005:280: lho phyogs su gshin rje ya ma r+aa dza sku mdog nag po stag lpags gyon pa /
NK037(ji)005:281: g.yas be con g.yon thod dbyug 'dzin pa /
NK037(ji)005:282: chibs su ma he sngon po la chibs pa /
NK037(ji)005:283: gshin rje 'bum gyi 'khor gyis bskor ba /
NK037(ji)005:284: nub phyogs su ma mo srid pa'i rgyal mo sku mdog nag mo brjid pa'i zhal can /
NK037(ji)005:285: sku la dar dkar gyi ral ga gsol ba /
NK037(ji)005:286: g.yas pas mda' dar g.yon pas me long bsnams pa /
NK037(ji)005:287: chibs su g.yu 'brug sngon po la chibs pa /
NK037(ji)005:288: ma mo 'bum gyi 'khor gyis bskor ba /
NK037(ji)005:289: byang phyogs su bdud pho skos rje brang dkar sku mdog mthing nag 'bar ba /
NK037(ji)005:290: sku la dar nag gi 'jol ber mnabs pa /
NK037(ji)005:291: g.yas pas khram shing g.yon pas dgra s+t+wa bsnams pa /
NK037(ji)005:292: chibs su bdud rta rting dkar la chibs pa /
NK037(ji)005:293: bdud dmag 'bum gyi 'khor gyis bskor ba /
NK037(ji)005:294: shar lho mtshams na btsan rje srog zan sku mdog
NK037(ji)005:295: dmar po sku la dar dmar le brgan gsol ba
NK037(ji)005:296: / g.yas pas mdung dar g.yon pas mda' gzhu bsnams pa /
NK037(ji)005:297: chibs su btsan rta dmar po la chibs pa /
NK037(ji)005:298: 'khor du btsan dmag 'bum gyi bskor ba /
NK037(ji)005:299: lho nub mtshams na dgra bla'i rgyal po pe har sku mdog dkar po brjid pa'i zhal mnga' ba /
NK037(ji)005:300: chos gos ngur smrig sku la gsol ba /
NK037(ji)005:301: g.yas gseg shang g.yon lhung bzed bsnams pa /
NK037(ji)005:302: chibs su seng ge dkar mo la chibs pa /
NK037(ji)005:304: nub byang mtshams na gnod sbyin k+aa la yak+sha sku mdog sngon po g.yu 'od 'bar ba /
NK037(ji)005:305: za 'og slog pa sku la gsol ba /
NK037(ji)005:306: g.yas pas ral gri g.yon pas nor bu 'dzin pa /
NK037(ji)005:307: chibs su stag mo drul ma la chibs pa /
NK037(ji)005:308: 'khor du gnod sbyin 'bum gyis bskor ba /
NK037(ji)005:309: byang shar mtshams na klu bdud 'chi bdag mgo dgu pa sku mdog dud kha 'jigs pa'i gzugs can /
NK037(ji)005:310: sku la sbrul gyi pags pa gyon pa /
NK037(ji)005:311: g.yas pas sbrul zhags g.yon pas nad rkyal bsnams pa /
NK037(ji)005:312: chibs su chu srin 'bar ba la chibs pa /
NK037(ji)005:313: 'khor du klu bdud 'bum gyis bskor ba /
NK037(ji)005:314: de'i phyi rol du gru chad bzhi la lha dmag bye ba dung phyur gyis bskor ba /
NK037(ji)005:315: thams cad kyi lus la go dang mtshon gyis brgyan pa'o //
NK037(ji)005:316: de'i phyir rol du dgra bla'i dmag tshogs bsam las 'das pas bskor ba /
NK037(ji)005:317: sgo bzhir rgyal po chen po sde bzhi g.yas pa
NK037(ji)005:318: thams cad kyis lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril
NK037(ji)005:319: bu bsnams pa / g.yon pa thams cad kyis rang rang gi rtags 'dzin pa'o //
NK037(ji)005:320: ri rab shar gyi bang rim dang po la dri za'i dmag tshogs /
NK037(ji)005:321: lho'i bang rim dang po la gshin rje'i dmag tshogs /
NK037(ji)005:322: nub kyi bang rim dang po la chu lha'i dmag tshogs /
NK037(ji)005:323: byang gi bang rim dang po la gnod sbyin gyi dmag tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK037(ji)005:324: bang rim bar ma bzhi la dpal mgon bdun cu
NK037(ji)005:325: la sogs pa'i gtsang rigs kyi mgon po rnams kyis
NK037(ji)005:326: bskor ba / bang rim tha ma bzhi la mgon po'i bka' sdod /
NK037(ji)005:336: nyi zla gza' skar gyi tshogs dang /
NK037(ji)005:345: phra men mgo brnyan gyi tshogs dang /
NK037(ji)005:346: gzhan yang sprul pa yang sprul gyi tshogs kyis bskor nas bzhugs par gyur /
NK037(ji)005:347: de dag thams cad kyang sku mdog sna tshogs pa phyag na mtshon cha sna tshogs 'dzin pa /
NK037(ji)005:348: lus thams cad go dang mtshon gyis brgyan nas dam
NK037(ji)005:349: nyams pa'i dgra bo'i tshe srog la rngam zhing rgyug
NK037(ji)005:351: gsum pa spyan drangs shing phyag dang mchod pa 'bul ba la bzhi ste /
NK037(ji)005:352: dang po snyan gsan dbab pa ni /
NK037(ji)005:353: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phros
NK037(ji)005:354: pas phyogs dus kyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK037(ji)005:355: chos sku zhi ba chen por bzhugs pa de /
NK037(ji)005:356: gzugs sku ma h+aa k+aa la'i tshul du bzhengs nas byon mdzad par bsam la /
NK037(ji)005:357: spos dang rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgya bca' la 'di skad do //
NK037(ji)005:361: na mo skyabs dam pa rnams kyi mchog /
NK037(ji)005:362: mgon dam pa rnams kyi gling /
NK037(ji)005:363: bsod nams thams cad kyi dpal zhing /
NK037(ji)005:364: yon tan thams cad kyi 'byung gnas /
NK037(ji)005:365: 'phags pa bla na ma mchis pa'i dkon mchog gsum po rnams dang /
NK037(ji)005:366: yi dam rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams dang /
NK037(ji)005:367: dam pa chos skyong ba'i srung ma'i tshogs ma lus pa rnams gsan cing dgongs su gsol /
NK037(ji)005:368: deng gi gnas mchog dam pa khyad par can 'dir spyan 'dren cing mchod pa 'bul /
NK037(ji)005:372: mthu chen nag po sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la /
NK037(ji)005:373: dug gsum nad kyi sman pa /
NK037(ji)005:376: bdud 'dul las kyi dbang phyug chen po /
NK037(ji)005:377: srin po lang ka pu ri'i grong khyer chen po
NK037(ji)005:378: gtan nas brlag par mdzad pa zhal gyis bzhes pa
NK037(ji)005:379: / phyag na tsan+dana gyi bing chen po zur brgyad
NK037(ji)005:380: pa bsnams pa'i nang nas lha dmag bye ba dung
NK037(ji)005:381: / phyur 'phro ba / lha ma yin gyi g.yul ngo zlog par mdzad cing /
NK037(ji)005:382: bdud 'dul lha dmag nyi khri chig stong 'byung ba /
NK037(ji)005:383: phyogs mtshams dang steng 'og thams cad la mnga' mdzad
NK037(ji)005:384: pa'i lha mgon po ma h+aa k+aa la'i tshogs rnams
NK037(ji)005:388: 'gro ba'i don phyir mchod kyis gshegs su gsol /
NK037(ji)005:389: bdag gi ci re ba dang ci smon pa thams
NK037(ji)005:390: cad las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzad du gsol
NK037(ji)005:391: / gnyis pa spyan drangs shing bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK037(ji)005:392: bdag gi thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer 'phros nas mdun gyi mgon po la phog /
NK037(ji)005:393: mgon po'i thugs ka nas 'od zer lcags kyu'i tshogs dpag tu med pa phyogs bcur 'phros pas /
NK037(ji)005:394: byang shar mtshams rang bzhin gyi gnas dang /
NK037(ji)005:397: sku gsung thugs kyi pho brang na bzhugs pa'i mgon po dang /
NK037(ji)005:398: mdung dang ral gri gshibs pa'i pho brang na mgon
NK037(ji)005:399: po 'khor dang bcas pa la phog pas sngon gyi
NK037(ji)005:400: da ma tshig dran nas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa
NK037(ji)005:401: srung ba'i dus la bab par dgongs nas /
NK037(ji)005:402: skad cig gis mdun gyi nam mkhar byon par bsam la /
NK037(ji)005:403: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la sa ma ya phem phem phem /
NK037(ji)005:404: zhes brgya rtsa brgyad brjod la spyan drangs pa ni rol mo dang bcas pas 'di skad do //
NK037(ji)005:406: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK037(ji)005:407: ma h+aa k+aa la spyan 'dren no //
NK037(ji)005:408: tshur gshegs tshul byon mgon po'i tshogs //
NK037(ji)005:409: dpal chen chos 'khor srung ma khyed //
NK037(ji)005:411: khyed kyi thugs dam dus la bab //
NK037(ji)005:412: bstan pa bsrung phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK037(ji)005:413: 'jigs byed chen po spyod pa rlabs chen drag shul
NK037(ji)005:414: mthu chen dgra bla'i rgyal po dus mtha' stongs byed
NK037(ji)005:415: 'chi bdag zlog byed khrag 'thung chen po legs ldan
NK037(ji)005:416: sras po rnal 'byor dgra bla dbang phyug chen po
NK037(ji)005:417: tshogs rje tshogs bdag dge bsnyen dam can 'jig rten
NK037(ji)005:418: mgon po dam tshig nye bar sems can don phyir
NK037(ji)005:419: bcom ldan thugs rje las byung ba'i //
NK037(ji)005:420: spyan ras gzigs kyi thugs rje che //
NK037(ji)005:421: ma h+aa k+aa la mthu chen khyed //
NK037(ji)005:422: srid pa'i ma mo'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK037(ji)005:423: srid gsum grong khyer sum brtsegs ni //
NK037(ji)005:424: 'dod khams gzugs khams gzugs med khams //
NK037(ji)005:425: khams gsum grong khyer sum brtsegs nas //
NK037(ji)005:427: gnas la chags pa'i rmongs pa sel //
NK037(ji)005:428: ma rig mun pa'i mdangs can la //
NK037(ji)005:429: phyin ci log lta bsal ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)005:430: mun pa sel phyir nag por ston //
NK037(ji)005:431: mthu stobs ldan zhing dbang phyug che //
NK037(ji)005:432: sred med bu dang stobs chen dang //
NK037(ji)005:433: gzhon nu smin drug bu la sogs //
NK037(ji)005:434: khyed kyi 'khor dang nye gnas yin //
NK037(ji)005:436: tshangs pa la sogs dbang phyug rnams //
NK037(ji)005:437: mthu dang dam tshig ldan na yang //
NK037(ji)005:438: khyod kyi spyod yul 'dra ba med //
NK037(ji)005:439: 'phags pa gsum gyis rjes bsgrub cing //
NK037(ji)005:440: zhing dang spyod yul dag pa yis //
NK037(ji)005:442: thugs dam bzhin du byin gyis barlobasa //
NK037(ji)005:443: ma h+aa k+aa la mthu bo che //
NK037(ji)005:444: rnal 'byor dgra blar gshegs pa'i tshe //
NK037(ji)005:445: dus gsum sangs rgyas dbang bskur rtags //
NK037(ji)005:446: sku yi cha byad gsum dang ldan //
NK037(ji)005:447: rigs gsum mgon pos dbang bskur rtags //
NK037(ji)005:448: dpral bar khro gnyer gsum dang ldan //
NK037(ji)005:449: dus gsum khro bos dbang bskur rtags //
NK037(ji)005:450: zhal gyi gdong ngar gsum dang ldan //
NK037(ji)005:451: drang srong rnams kyis mnga' gsol rtags //
NK037(ji)005:452: chos gos sham thabs sku la gsol //
NK037(ji)005:453: lha chen rnams kyis mnga' gsol rtags //
NK037(ji)005:454: rin chen 'bar ba'i thor tshugs can //
NK037(ji)005:455: klu chen rnams kyis mnga' gsol rtags //
NK037(ji)005:456: yan lag sbrul chun chun pos brgyan //
NK037(ji)005:457: gza' chen rnams kyis mnga' gsol ral pa dmar ser me ltar 'bar //
NK037(ji)005:458: lha rnams kun gyis bswo sgra drag po gsum dang ldan //
NK037(ji)005:459: rgyu skar rnams kyis tshe lo sme ba se ral kha //
NK037(ji)005:460: lha ma yin gyis mnga' cha sgra drag po gsum dang ldan //
NK037(ji)005:461: byol song rnams kyis mnga' 'dod dgu phun sum tshogs pas brgyan //
NK037(ji)005:462: yi dwags rnams kyis rin chen 'bar ba'i do shal can //
NK037(ji)005:463: mi rnams kun gyis rin chen sna lngas sku la brgyan //
NK037(ji)005:464: dmyal ba rnams kyis thod pa'i phreng bas sku la brgyan //
NK037(ji)005:465: ag+ni r+aa dzas spyan nas bskal pa'i me chen 'bar //
NK037(ji)005:466: bi n+aa ya kas mnga' zhal nas bskal pa'i chu chen 'khyil //
NK037(ji)005:467: p+aa yu r+aa dzas mnga' shangs nas bskal pa'i rlung nag 'tshubs //
NK037(ji)005:468: bdud rnams kun gyi mnga' rgya ber nag po sku
NK037(ji)005:469: la gnab gshin rje rnams kyis phyag na tsan+da na
NK037(ji)005:470: bing chen bsnams // ma mo rnams kyis thod pa'i phreng ba se ral kha //
NK037(ji)005:471: srid pa gsum gyis mnga' gsol rtags //
NK037(ji)005:472: sku yi lte ba zur gsum zab /
NK037(ji)005:473: lha chen dpal 'bar gshegs su gsol //
NK037(ji)005:474: ri rab zom la ljur gyis byon //
NK037(ji)005:475: tsan+dana bing chen klad la bskor //
NK037(ji)005:476: bswo sgra thang gsum gnam du btang //
NK037(ji)005:477: lha rnams g.yul las rgyal bar byed //
NK037(ji)005:478: lha min g.yul rnams pham par byed //
NK037(ji)005:479: byang shar mtshams nas spyan 'dren na //
NK037(ji)005:480: rlung nag 'tshubs ma'i nang nas gshegs //
NK037(ji)005:481: sprin phung 'dus pa'i nang na bzhugs //
NK037(ji)005:482: ma h+aa k+aa la 'khor bcas rnams //
NK037(ji)005:483: sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK037(ji)005:484: dam tshig dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK037(ji)005:485: zhes phyogs bcu'i brgyan thams cad ma h+aa k+aa la'i tshogs su gyur nas /
NK037(ji)005:486: dam tshig dbang gis byon nas sangs rgyas kyi bstan
NK037(ji)005:487: pa la gnod par byed pa'i dgra bo thams cad
NK037(ji)005:489: mdun gyi nam mkhar byon par bsam la /
NK037(ji)005:490: e h+ye hi sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la dzahmh'u bam hoh +aa gats+tsha ya +aa gats+tsha ya /
NK037(ji)005:491: tish+tha badz+ra sa ma ya h'u /
NK037(ji)005:493: ye shes pa rnams dam tshig pa la mtsho la
NK037(ji)005:494: kha ba bab pa bzhin du yang yang bstim mo
NK037(ji)005:495: // de nas byin gyis brlab pa dang dbang bskur ni /
NK037(ji)005:496: +aahmh'u gis sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab /
NK037(ji)005:497: e rdu pa e badz+ra san+ta hri la pa h+r+aih u ni ni e lam mi ni h'u /
NK037(ji)005:498: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta a b+hi shiny+tsan+tu m+aam /
NK037(ji)005:499: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis lha tshogs rnams kyi spyi bor dbang bskur /
NK037(ji)005:500: lus ngag yid gsum gyi dri ma dag /
NK037(ji)005:501: chu'i lhag ma yar lud pa las /
NK037(ji)005:502: tshogs bdag la tho rangs skar chen ltar spyan ras gzigs kyis dbu brgyan /
NK037(ji)005:503: gtso bo la rigs lngas dbu brgyan /
NK037(ji)005:504: yum la yum lngas dbu brgyan /
NK037(ji)005:505: spyan ras gzigs la 'od dpag med kyis dbu brgyan /
NK037(ji)005:506: sku mchog la gshin rje'i gshed kyis dbu brgyan /
NK037(ji)005:507: gsung mchog la rta mgrin gyis dbu brgyan /
NK037(ji)005:508: thugs mchog la phyag na rdo rjes dbu brgyan pa'o //
NK037(ji)005:510: lha mi thams cad kyi ded dpon du dbang bskur bas /
NK037(ji)005:511: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa thams cad
NK037(ji)005:512: kyi nus mthu thams cad bsdus nas bkrag mdangs dang
NK037(ji)005:515: rang gi thugs ka nas shes pa gnyis su phyes
NK037(ji)005:516: la cha gcig la mchod pa'i lha mo dpag tu
NK037(ji)005:518: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa bsrung ba dang /
NK037(ji)005:519: dgra bgegs gdug pa can bsgral ba dang /
NK037(ji)005:520: rnal 'byor pa bdag la dngos grub stsol ba'i don
NK037(ji)005:521: du lha dmag gis gtso byas 'khor rnams la phyag
NK037(ji)005:522: 'tshal / 'khor rnams kyis tshogs bdag 'khor bcas la
NK037(ji)005:523: sgo gsum gus pa'i tshul du phyag 'tshal bar bsam
NK037(ji)005:526: lha min dmag tshogs g.yul zlog cing //
NK037(ji)005:527: lha dmag dkar po dbugs 'byin pa //
NK037(ji)005:528: ma h+aa k+aa la 'khor bcas la //
NK037(ji)005:529: mchod cing bstod de phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)005:530: zla ba'i 'od ltar zhal gsal ba //
NK037(ji)005:531: ma rig sgrib pa spang ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)005:533: tshogs bdag khyed la lha rnams kun gyis ma mchod tshe //
NK037(ji)005:534: lha rnams g.yul las rgyal ma gyur //
NK037(ji)005:535: mchod nas g.yul las rgyal ba thob //
NK037(ji)005:536: tshogs bdag khyed la lha rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK037(ji)005:537: khyed la lhas kyang thog mar mchod //
NK037(ji)005:538: mchod 'os rnams kyis mchod mdzad pa //
NK037(ji)005:539: tshogs bdag dkon mchog gsum gyi gzungs bzlas pas //
NK037(ji)005:540: don dam phun sum tshogs 'grub cing //
NK037(ji)005:541: rgyal ba rnams kyi lung bstan pa //
NK037(ji)005:542: tshogs bdag ston pa'i bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)005:543: mtshan du rdo rje 'chang ngo zhes //
NK037(ji)005:544: dbang bskur gang gis gtsor gyur pa //
NK037(ji)005:545: tshogs bdag khyed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)005:546: yon tan bsam 'das brjod mi lang //
NK037(ji)005:547: sems can ma rig don slad du //
NK037(ji)005:548: mchod bstod tshogs bdag mnyes gyur cig /
NK037(ji)005:549: tshogs rje tshogs bdag chen po khyed //
NK037(ji)005:550: mgon po bzhugs gnas dkyil 'khor du //
NK037(ji)005:551: bla med mchod pa'i sprin 'byung zhing //
NK037(ji)005:552: yon tan brgyad ldan thams cad kyis //
NK037(ji)005:553: zhabs la spyi bos gtugs gyur cig /
NK037(ji)005:554: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la ya /
NK037(ji)005:555: a ti pu hoh pra t+aits+tsha hoh bzhi pa mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK037(ji)005:556: phyi mchod rnam lnga nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags dang phyag rgyas byin gyis brlab /
NK037(ji)005:557: nang mchod rnam lnga sman raka gtor gsum sha lnga bdud rtsi lngar byin gyis brlabs la /
NK037(ji)005:558: rang gi thugs ka nas mchod pa'i lha mo dpag tu med pa spros pas /
NK037(ji)005:559: bshams pa'i mchod rdzas thams cad 'dod yon dpag tu
NK037(ji)005:560: med pas nam mkha' sa gzhi bar snang thams cad
NK037(ji)005:561: gang nas / mgon po 'khor dang bcas pa la phul bas mnyes shing tshims par bsam la /
NK037(ji)005:563: dpal ldan mgon po mthu chen khyod //
NK037(ji)005:564: yon tan byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK037(ji)005:565: 'phags pa'i thugs rjes mnga' brnyes kyang //
NK037(ji)005:566: dus ngan sems can 'dul slad du //
NK037(ji)005:567: dkon mchog gsum gyi sku srung zhing //
NK037(ji)005:568: skye 'gro yongs kyi skyabs kyang mdzad //
NK037(ji)005:569: phyag na bdud 'dul bing chen bsnams //
NK037(ji)005:570: bskal pa'i me ltar gzi brjid 'bar //
NK037(ji)005:571: yun gyi mgon dang mthur bsten gyi //
NK037(ji)005:573: rtag tu srung zhing bskyab tu gsol //
NK037(ji)005:574: dkyil 'khor mdzes pa dam pa dang //
NK037(ji)005:575: me tog phreng ba rin chen dbyig /
NK037(ji)005:576: yon chab bdug spos mar me dang //
NK037(ji)005:577: dri dang lha bshos byug pa gos //
NK037(ji)005:578: gzugs mdzes sgra snyan dri zhim dang //
NK037(ji)005:579: ro dang reg bya 'jam la sogs //
NK037(ji)005:580: sna tshogs mchod pa 'di dag bzhes //
NK037(ji)005:581: thugs rjes 'gro ba'i don la dgongs //
NK037(ji)005:582: bdag cag re zhing smon pa rnams //
NK037(ji)005:584: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la sa pa ri b+aa ra
NK037(ji)005:585: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK037(ji)005:586: khe b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham at+ga te s+pha ra na i
NK037(ji)005:587: mam ga ga na kham gri h+ne i dam ba
NK037(ji)005:589: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la yak+sha be t+aa li ma h+aa sarba pany+tsa a mri ta la kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)005:590: ma h+aa rak+ta la kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)005:591: ma h+aa ba lim ta la kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)005:592: dgra bgegs ming dang gzugs su bris pa rnams kyi ma h+aa m+aam sa la kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)005:593: ma h+aa rak+ta la kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)005:594: ma h+aa tsit+ta la ma h+aa ba su ta la
NK037(ji)005:595: ma h+aa go ro tsa na la ma h+aa kim
NK037(ji)005:596: ni ri ti la dbang po rnam lnga la don
NK037(ji)005:597: snying nang rol la sha khrag srog dbugs la rnam
NK037(ji)005:598: shes tshogs brgyad la skye mched bcu gnyis la lhag
NK037(ji)005:599: ma rjes shul la kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)005:607: shap+da pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK037(ji)005:608: sdang ba'i dgra dang gnod pa'i bgegs //
NK037(ji)005:609: nag po chen po'i zhal du stob //
NK037(ji)005:610: slob dpon sku la bsdo ba dang //
NK037(ji)005:611: rnal 'byor bdag la sdang ba dang //
NK037(ji)005:612: rdo rje spun la 'khu ba dang //
NK037(ji)005:613: bdag gi 'khor la gnod pa dang /
NK037(ji)005:614: ming dang gzugs su bris pa 'di //
NK037(ji)005:615: nag po chen po'i zhal du stob //
NK037(ji)005:616: yan lag rnams kyi sha chod la //
NK037(ji)005:617: mgon po chen po'i zhal du rol //
NK037(ji)005:618: tshe srog dmar po rtsad nas chod //
NK037(ji)005:619: khrag gi rgyun yang 'thung bar byed //
NK037(ji)005:620: snying khrag drod mo zhal du gsol //
NK037(ji)005:621: til 'bru tsam yang med par mdzod //
NK037(ji)005:623: mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma rgya chen po 'di mchod cing 'bul ba'i gnas ni /
NK037(ji)005:626: dug gsum nad kyi sman pa /
NK037(ji)005:630: phyi nang gnyis kyi tshogs bdag /
NK037(ji)005:632: sku gsung thugs kyi mgon po /
NK037(ji)005:637: lha dmag bye ba dung phyur dang bcas pa rnams la mchod do //
NK037(ji)005:643: 'dod pa'i yon tan gyi tshogs kyis mnyes par mdzod /
NK037(ji)005:644: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa rnams la bsrung zhing bskyab pa dang /
NK037(ji)005:645: bsam smon thams cad yid bzhin du 'grub par mdzad du gsol /
NK037(ji)005:646: phrin las su bcol ba'i mdo ni /
NK037(ji)005:647: nyi ma phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad kyi dgra bgegs gdug
NK037(ji)005:648: pa can sdang sems dang ldan pa ming gzugs su
NK037(ji)005:649: bris pa rnams thal ba'i rdul phran bzhin du brlag
NK037(ji)005:651: ces brjod pa tsam gyis sman raka gtor ma la
NK037(ji)005:652: sogs mchod rdzas thams cad 'dod yon gyi tshogs su
NK037(ji)005:653: gyur nas / mgon po'i lha tshogs rnams la phul bas mnyes nas /
NK037(ji)005:654: ljags gri gug gi sbu gur gyur nas gsol bar bsam la 'bul lo //
NK037(ji)005:655: lnga pa bstod pa bya ba ni /
NK037(ji)005:656: mgon po'i rgyan cha lugs ji ltar ba bzhin du gsal gdab la /
NK037(ji)005:657: 'khor rnams kyis gtso bo la lus ngag yid gsum
NK037(ji)005:658: gyi sgo nas phyag dang bstod pa byed par bsam
NK037(ji)005:659: la / rnga drag rdung gsum dang ldan par byas la 'di skad do //
NK037(ji)005:661: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i dbus //
NK037(ji)005:662: dur khrod chen po'i gnas mchog na //
NK037(ji)005:663: dpal ldan mgon po nag po ni //
NK037(ji)005:664: sku mdog mthing nag char sprin mdog /
NK037(ji)005:665: bam chen steng na 'gying bag can //
NK037(ji)005:666: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum dmar //
NK037(ji)005:667: ral pa dmar ser mche ba gtsigs //
NK037(ji)005:668: sku la dar nag 'jog ber mnabs //
NK037(ji)005:669: phyag g.yas tsan+dana bing chen phyar //
NK037(ji)005:670: g.yon pas thod pa khrag bkang gsol //
NK037(ji)005:671: gser ska ser po'i ske rags bcings //
NK037(ji)005:672: zhabs la sag ti'i lhwam sngon man bas //
NK037(ji)005:673: bskal pa'i me ri'i klong nas bzhengs //
NK037(ji)005:674: bstan pa bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK037(ji)005:675: dpal ldan mgon po nag po che //
NK037(ji)005:676: ral pa gyen du 'bar ba yis //
NK037(ji)005:677: steng gi lha bdud zlog par byed //
NK037(ji)005:678: dpral bar khro gnyer gsum ldan pas //
NK037(ji)005:679: srid gsum bgegs rnams zlog par byed //
NK037(ji)005:680: mche ba zur gsum gtsigs pa yis //
NK037(ji)005:681: bdud bzhi'i bar chad zlog par byed //
NK037(ji)005:682: dar nag 'jol ber gsol ba yis //
NK037(ji)005:683: tshe bdud nag po zlog par byed //
NK037(ji)005:684: tsan+dana bing chen phyar ba yis //
NK037(ji)005:685: lha min g.yul ngo zlog par byed //
NK037(ji)005:686: g.yon pas thod khrag bsnams pa yis //
NK037(ji)005:687: dgra bgegs snying khrag 'thung bar byed //
NK037(ji)005:688: gser ska ser pos ske rags bcings pa ni //
NK037(ji)005:689: rnal 'byor bar chad zlog par byed //
NK037(ji)005:690: g.yas bskum g.yon brkyang byed pa ni //
NK037(ji)005:691: 'chi bdag gshin rje zlog par byed //
NK037(ji)005:692: bam chen steng na 'gying ba ni //
NK037(ji)005:693: sa bdag klu gnyan zlog par byed //
NK037(ji)005:694: bskal pa'i me dpung klong na 'gying pa ni //
NK037(ji)005:695: nyon mongs bag chags ma lus sreg par byed //
NK037(ji)005:696: zlog byed rgyal po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK037(ji)005:697: zlog byed nag po 'khor bcas la //
NK037(ji)005:698: bdag gi mchod cing bstod nas ni //
NK037(ji)005:699: bka' 'khor srungs la bar chad zlog /
NK037(ji)005:700: sangs rgyas bstan pa bshig pa dang //
NK037(ji)005:701: dkon mchog dbu 'phang smad pa dang //
NK037(ji)005:702: slob dpon sku la bsdo ba dang //
NK037(ji)005:703: bdag la bar du gcod pa yi //
NK037(ji)005:704: sdang ba'i dgra dang gnod pa'i bgegs //
NK037(ji)005:705: thams cad ma lus rdul du rlog /
NK037(ji)005:706: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK037(ji)005:708: bskal pa me rlung 'tshubs ma'i klong dkyil nas //
NK037(ji)005:709: smon lam stobs kyis sangs rgyas bstan pa srung //
NK037(ji)005:710: dpal ldan lha mo nag mo ni //
NK037(ji)005:711: sku mdog mthing nag mun ltar gtibs //
NK037(ji)005:712: khrag gi ral pa g.yas g.yon 'khyil //
NK037(ji)005:713: phyag g.yas gcod byed gri gug phyar //
NK037(ji)005:714: g.yon pas thod khrag nad rkyal bsnams //
NK037(ji)005:715: chibs su dre'u nag gwa pa chibs //
NK037(ji)005:717: dam rdzas rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK037(ji)005:718: dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK037(ji)005:720: sku yi mgon po gtum byed ni //
NK037(ji)005:721: sku mdog mthing nag char sprin 'dra //
NK037(ji)005:722: phyag gnyis rtse gsum thod khrag bsnams //
NK037(ji)005:723: dgra bo'i snying khrag zhal du gsol //
NK037(ji)005:725: sku mchog khyed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK037(ji)005:727: gsung gi mgon po gsod byed ni //
NK037(ji)005:728: sku la dar nag ber chen brgyan //
NK037(ji)005:729: phyag gnyis bing dang thod khrag bsnams //
NK037(ji)005:730: dgra bo'i srog rtsa gcod par byed //
NK037(ji)005:731: gshin rje'i tshogs kyi gdug pa 'dul //
NK037(ji)005:732: gsung mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK037(ji)005:734: thugs kyi mgon po sgrol byed ni //
NK037(ji)005:735: sku ni rngams brjid mthing nag la //
NK037(ji)005:736: phyag gnyis gri gug thod khrag bsnams //
NK037(ji)005:737: sdang byed dgra bgegs dgug cing gsod //
NK037(ji)005:738: ma mo'i tshogs kyi gdug pa 'dul //
NK037(ji)005:739: thugs mchog khyed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK037(ji)005:741: lha dmag bye ba'i tshogs rnams ni //
NK037(ji)005:742: dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i don ched du //
NK037(ji)005:743: zhal nas cha sgra di ri ri //
NK037(ji)005:744: dgra bgegs bzlog pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK037(ji)005:746: phyogs skyong bcu po 'khor dang bcas //
NK037(ji)005:747: bka' yi lha srin sde brgyad dang //
NK037(ji)005:748: mkha' la rgyu ba ma mo'i tshogs //
NK037(ji)005:749: 'gal rkyen zlog la dngos grub stsol //
NK037(ji)005:751: yang sprul pho nya'i tshogs rnams ni //
NK037(ji)005:752: mtshon cha sna tshogs phyag na bsnams //
NK037(ji)005:753: dgra bgegs srog rtsa gcod cing gtubs //
NK037(ji)005:754: mi mthun rkyen dang bar chad zlog /
NK037(ji)005:755: mthun pa'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK037(ji)005:756: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK037(ji)005:758: bde gshegs mgon po bstan pa'i dpal //
NK037(ji)005:759: tshogs bdag dgyes pa'i byin rlabs las //
NK037(ji)005:760: sdug bsngal nad sel thugs rje che //
NK037(ji)005:761: thams cad sprul pa'i cho 'phrul dpal //
NK037(ji)005:762: tshogs rje tshogs kyi bdag po ste //
NK037(ji)005:763: de bzhin gshegs pa bzhed par ston //
NK037(ji)005:764: khams gsum khengs pa'i sems can rnams //
NK037(ji)005:765: tshe dang srog la dbang ba ste //
NK037(ji)005:766: shes rab mtshon gyis sgyu mar ston //
NK037(ji)005:767: blun rmongs khengs pa thal bar mdzod //
NK037(ji)005:768: mi mthun phyogs rnams zad par ston //
NK037(ji)005:769: byang chub chen por khyed kyis sgrol //
NK037(ji)005:770: dpal gyi snying po dpal phreng ma //
NK037(ji)005:771: dpal gyi tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK037(ji)005:772: de nas smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK037(ji)005:773: yon mchod kun gyis thal mo sbyar ba'i bar du me tog thogs la /
NK037(ji)005:774: bing gi rtse mo las yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che'i char babs pas /
NK037(ji)005:775: gnas khang thams cad gang bar bsgom /
NK037(ji)005:776: gzhung nas ji ltar bshad bzhin smon pa'i don thams
NK037(ji)005:777: cad lha tshogs rnams kyis sgrub par bsam la 'di
NK037(ji)005:779: mgon po khyed mchod byin rlabs kyis //
NK037(ji)005:780: phyogs dang dus kun thams cad du //
NK037(ji)005:781: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK037(ji)005:782: phyogs bcu gang du 'gro na yang //
NK037(ji)005:783: gnod byed dgra bgegs med par mdzod //
NK037(ji)005:784: nad dang gnod pa kun bral nas //
NK037(ji)005:785: bgegs kyi gnod pa kun med shog /
NK037(ji)005:786: rta dang ba glang nor dang 'bru //
NK037(ji)005:787: bu dang bu mo gnyen bshes rnams //
NK037(ji)005:788: dge zhing tshe ring bder spyod pa'i //
NK037(ji)005:789: longs spyod phun sum tshogs par shog /
NK037(ji)005:790: rgyal po mya ngan med pa bzhin //
NK037(ji)005:791: chos kyi rgyal srid skyong bar shog /
NK037(ji)005:792: bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa 'di //
NK037(ji)005:793: phyogs bcu kun tu dar ba dang //
NK037(ji)005:794: myur du sems can thams cad kyang //
NK037(ji)005:795: bdud rtsi'i snod du 'gyur bar shog /
NK037(ji)005:796: dge ba thams cad phyir bsngosa dang //
NK037(ji)005:797: mgon po khyed mchod byin rlabs kyis //
NK037(ji)005:798: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa yi //
NK037(ji)005:799: longs spyod thams cad rdzogs par shog /
NK037(ji)005:800: bdag kyang byang chub mchog thob nas //
NK037(ji)005:801: mgon po khyed dang mi 'bral 'grogs par shog /
NK037(ji)005:802: ye d+har+m+aa he tu pra b+h+aa ba he tun+te sh+aan+ta
NK037(ji)005:803: th+aa ga to h+ya ba data te sh+aany+tsa yo ni
NK037(ji)005:804: ro d+ha e w+aam b+aa d+ai ma h+aa sh+r+aa ma
NK037(ji)005:805: nahswa h+aa / bdag gi thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer 'phros pas tshogs bdag la phog pas /
NK037(ji)005:806: tshogs bdag gtso 'khor las 'od zer ser po'i tshogs dpag tu med pa 'phros nas byung bas /
NK037(ji)005:807: bdag cag la phog pa tsam gyis tshe dang bsod
NK037(ji)005:808: nams dpal dang 'byor pa bkra shis pa'i rtags brgyad
NK037(ji)005:809: rgyal srid sna bdun la sogs 'dod yon sna tshogs
NK037(ji)005:811: bkra shis bde legs phun sum tshogs par bsam /
NK037(ji)005:813: rang nyid yi dam gyi thugs ka'i sngags phreng gi
NK037(ji)005:814: phyi rol du mgon po'i sngags kyis 'khor bar dmigs
NK037(ji)005:815: / yum la yang de ltar dmigs la /
NK037(ji)005:816: thog mar dbang du bsdu zhing zil gyis gnon pa'i sngags 'di bgrang ngo //
NK037(ji)005:817: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la ga na gu ti ka ma la sh+r+ai nag mo ti la b+h+yo /
NK037(ji)005:818: ces brgya rtsa brgyad la sogs pa mang du bzlas pas srog gi snying po phul bar bsgom mo //
NK037(ji)005:819: de nas bsnyen pa bya ba ni /
NK037(ji)005:820: de yang gnad kyi man ngag dam pa dgos te /
NK037(ji)005:822: lnga 'dus dang po 'od kyi gong bu na //
NK037(ji)005:823: rtsa 'dus las kyi 'brel ba'i srog snying phul //
NK037(ji)005:825: bdag he ru ka'i thugs ka'i h'u gi rgyab tu
NK037(ji)005:826: sngags 'khor las 'od zer kha dog sna lnga'i gur
NK037(ji)005:827: che chung bya ma gsar gyi sgo nga tsam gcig
NK037(ji)005:828: bsam / de las 'od zer 'phros pas tshogs bdag gi spyi bor spyan ras gzigs la phog /
NK037(ji)005:829: de las 'od zer mar 'phros nas tshogs bdag la phog pas sngon gyi dam tshig dran nas /
NK037(ji)005:830: de'i 'od zer 'khor thams cad la rim bzhin du phog /
NK037(ji)005:831: 'khor rnams kyis sngon gyi dam tshig dran nas 'dar phri li li byed cing dran pa bskul nas /
NK037(ji)005:832: de rnams kyi srog snying de 'od kha dog sna
NK037(ji)005:833: lnga'i tshul du gcig gis gcig bskul nas yar phul
NK037(ji)005:834: nas las mgon gsum la phul /
NK037(ji)005:835: las mgon gsum gyis de rnams kyis phul ba'i srog snying thams cad dang /
NK037(ji)005:836: rang rang gi srog gi snying po 'od kyi rnam
NK037(ji)005:837: pa de yang rim pa bzhin du brgyud nas mgon
NK037(ji)005:838: po la phul / mgon pos sngon gyi dam tshig
NK037(ji)005:839: dran nas bdag gi bka' nyan gsung sdod cing bcol
NK037(ji)005:840: ba'i las thams cad myur du byed par khas blangs
NK037(ji)005:841: po la phul / dam bcas nas / srog gi
NK037(ji)005:842: snying po yi ge h'u gi tshul du bdag la
NK037(ji)005:843: phul nas thugs ka'i h'u gi zhabs kyu nang du
NK037(ji)005:845: srog snying gta' ru bzung ba'i man ngag go //
NK037(ji)005:846: yang bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer lcags kyu lta bu dpag tu med pa 'phros pas /
NK037(ji)005:847: mgon po 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs kar phog pas
NK037(ji)005:848: de rnams kyi srog gi snying po mdongs gsol du
NK037(ji)005:849: phul ba ni nyi ma'i zer ra ma gdugs rtsibs
NK037(ji)005:850: bzhin du bdag gi thugs kar 'dus par bsam la
NK037(ji)005:851: / sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la h'u phata /
NK037(ji)005:852: 'di ni yab kyi bsnyen pa'am 'bod pa'o //
NK037(ji)005:853: ma h+aa k+aa la sid+d+hi yam du dzah bsnyen pa 'di ni rang la myur bar 'dug go //
NK037(ji)005:854: rlung ltar mgyogs pa'i dngos grub kyi rtse mo'o //
NK037(ji)005:855: badz+ra yak+sha be t+aa li h'u /
NK037(ji)005:857: trag rak+sha rak+mo thum lam snying la 'dus 'dus /
NK037(ji)005:858: srog la bring bring sham sham khyer b+h+yo /
NK037(ji)005:859: drag sngags 'dis ni 'jig rten gsum gyi ma mo 'adu'o //
NK037(ji)005:860: yab kyi thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du h'u gi mtha' mar sngags kyi 'khor ba'o //
NK037(ji)005:861: yum la b+h+yo'i mtha' mar sngags kyis 'khor ba'o //
NK037(ji)005:863: yab yum 'khor dang bcas pa'i zhal nas rang sngags di ri ri brjod par bsam la /
NK037(ji)005:864: yab la stong bsnyen na yum la brgya /
NK037(ji)005:865: yab la khri bsnyen na yum la stong /
NK037(ji)005:866: yab la 'bum bsnyen na yum la khri bsnyen no //
NK037(ji)005:867: nyin par yab kyi snyen pa bya /
NK037(ji)005:868: nub mo yum gyi bsnyen pa byed do //
NK037(ji)005:869: thun bzhag pa'i thun mtshams su phyi nang gi mchod pas mchod la /
NK037(ji)005:872: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i dbus //
NK037(ji)005:873: dur khrod chen po'i gnas mchog nas //
NK037(ji)005:874: bam chen steng na 'gying bag can //
NK037(ji)005:875: dpal ldan mgon po nag po ni //
NK037(ji)005:876: bdud dang dgra bgegs bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK037(ji)005:877: byams pa'i sems kyis mchod 'bul bstod //
NK037(ji)005:878: de ltar bsnyen pa'i rtags ni /
NK037(ji)005:879: rnal 'byor pa rab mngon sum du 'ong ste /
NK037(ji)005:880: zhal dngos su bstan pa dang /
NK037(ji)005:885: rdo rje slob dpon 'ong ba dang /
NK037(ji)005:886: dge bshes chen po 'ong ba dang /
NK037(ji)005:888: de la sogs pa rtags dang cho 'phrul dngos su 'ong /
NK037(ji)005:891: rtags med na dam tshig nyams pa yin pas ba lim bzang du bsham /
NK037(ji)005:893: tshogs mchod dang spang skong zhi khro 'don /
NK037(ji)005:894: bsnyen pa nam bzhag pa'i dus su phyi nang gi mchod pa 'bul la bstod pa byed /
NK037(ji)005:896: de yan chad stod las byang chub bsgrub pa'o //
NK037(ji)005:897: 'dir smad las dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i las rim ni gzhan du shes par bya /
NK037(ji)005:898: de nas 'khor rnams rim pa bzhin du las mgon gsum la bsdu /
NK037(ji)005:899: las mgon rnams gtso bo yab yum la bsdu /
NK037(ji)005:900: gtso bo yab yum bing la bsdu /
NK037(ji)005:902: h'u rang nyid yi dam gyi lte bar thim par bsgom /
NK037(ji)005:903: yi dam 'khor bcas rim gyis bsdu la /
NK037(ji)005:905: de nas rim pa bzhin du mi dmigs pa'i rgyas gdab /
NK037(ji)005:906: de'i ngang la h'u brjod pa tsam gyis /
NK037(ji)005:907: skad cig gis rang nyid yi dam zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa gcig gsal bar bskyed do //
NK037(ji)005:908: de ltar byas pas chos skyong 'grub thag nye ba dang /
NK037(ji)005:910: tshe ring longs spyod 'phel bar byed do //
NK037(ji)005:911: mgon po legs ldan 'di la sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud gsum yod pa de la /
NK037(ji)005:912: sku yi rgyud bing chen brtsegs pa'i rgyud /
NK037(ji)005:913: gsung rgyud khrag mtsho khol ma'i rgyud /
NK037(ji)005:914: thugs rgyud gri gug bsnol ma'i rgyud dang gsum las /
NK037(ji)005:915: 'di ni bing chen brtsegs pa'i rgyud do //
NK037(ji)005:916: de'i nang nas drag sngags gsang ba'i spu gri 'di zab zer nas gnang ngo //
NK037(ji)005:923: bsam yas su btsad po khri srong lde'u btsan /
NK037(ji)005:924: sku lha stong bkra shis kyi dgon pa na slob dpon bee ro tsa na byon pa'i tshe na /
NK037(ji)005:925: rnal 'byor pa nyang sha mi go cha bya ba
NK037(ji)005:926: gcig gis gser srang bdun phul nas bstan pa srung
NK037(ji)005:927: ba'i chos skyong gcig zhu 'tshal zhes zhus pa las
NK037(ji)005:928: / de yang drag sngags gsang ba'i spu gri 'di nyid gnang /
NK037(ji)005:929: rnal 'byor pa des kyang de ma thag tu sgrub
NK037(ji)005:930: pa mdzad pas zhag bdun nas tshogs bdag zhal mjal
NK037(ji)005:931: nas yi dam gyi lhar gyur /
NK037(ji)005:932: sro thog rgyal po'i dben gnas su slob dpon phyin tsa na /
NK037(ji)005:933: ldi ri chos kyi grags pas chos skyong gcig zhus pas /
NK037(ji)005:934: 'di gnang nas des kyang de ma thag tu sgrub
NK037(ji)005:935: pas zhal mthong nas shin tu mnyes nas bee ro
NK037(ji)005:936: tsa na la gser srang bcu phul skad /
NK037(ji)005:937: yang slob dpon ba thang shing rgyal ba'i dben gnas su phyin tsa na /
NK037(ji)005:938: mkha' 'gro ma b+ha ra ka si bya ba gcig
NK037(ji)005:939: gis chos skyong gcig zhu byas pas nag po chen
NK037(ji)005:941: de ma thag tu bsgrubs nas zhal mthong bar gda' /
NK037(ji)005:942: gser srang bcu phul nas shin tu mnyes skad /
NK037(ji)005:943: de nas rtse sgong skyes kyi yang dgon du phyin tsa na /
NK037(ji)005:944: g.yu sgra snying po dang snying mo gnyis kyis slob
NK037(ji)005:945: dpon la phrin las kyi lha gcig zhu byas pa
NK037(ji)005:946: la nag po chen po 'di gnang skad /
NK037(ji)005:947: ma h+aa k+aa la'i zhal mthong nas rjes su yi rang ngo //
NK037(ji)005:948: de nas so sor rim par brgyud de bdag la'o //

NK037(ji)005:954: dam can srung ma rgya mtsho'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK037(ji)005:955: bzod par bzhes nas tshangs par stsal du gsol //
NK037(ji)005:956: 'di bris dge bas mkha' khyab sems can rnams //
NK037(ji)005:957: sa lam stan thog gcig tu bgrod nas kyang //
NK037(ji)005:958: 'phags mgon khyod kyi sa la gnas pa dang //
NK037(ji)005:959: sku lnga lhun grub sangs rgyas myur thob shog /
NK037(ji)005:961: bee ro tsa na gnyis kyi snyan brgyud /
NK037(ji)005:962: slob dpon bee ro tsa nas ci bshad bzhin du
NK037(ji)005:963: bdag ldi ri chos kyi grags pas gsang ba'i spu
NK037(ji)005:964: gri'i rgyud dang / las rim la brten nas nyams
NK037(ji)005:965: su len thabs dbri bsnan med par gong 'og bsdebs
NK037(ji)005:966: nas yi ger bkod pa rdzogs so ////
